# outputs/

This folder is generated by the R analysis pipeline.

Run `source("R/run_all.R")` from the project root to populate it with:

- `dashboard_full.png` — 6-panel analysis dashboard
- `p1_coverage_forecast.png`
- `p2_afp_cases.png`
- `p3_dropout_rate.png`
- `p4_zero_dose.png`
- `p5_annual_coverage.png`
- `p6_stl_decomposition.png`
- `annual_summary.csv`
- `district_comparison.csv`
- `coverage_forecasts.csv`
- `afp_forecasts.csv`
